          "level": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "You can build your own custom components for the Keystone's document field and use them in the Rich Text Editor while authoring content. You have complete control over how your custom components are authored in the editor and how you render them on your website. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "When it comes to what you can do with custom components, your imagination is your only limit. Here are a few example custom components I've created —"
            }
